Rest API

City Service
--------------

Resource   :   city

CRUD
|_ POST  -  Create
|_ GET   -  Retreive
|_ PUT   - Update
|_ DELETE - Delete

endpoint/url:

/city    GET, POST, DELETE

/city/<cityID> GET, PUT, DELETE

custom queries:  [query/request/application parameter]

return all the cities with population above 5lakhs

/city?population=5000000

return first 5 cities
/city?start=1&size=5


Retreive a city with id
/city/1001
/city?cityID=1001   x  





